OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FElectric car charging costs
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fnear petrol, says RAC      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The cost of charging an electric car   
OL,6, has surged due to the rise in energy   
OL,7, prices, prompting fears it will put off
OL,8, drivers from buying them, the RAC said.
OL,10,FIt said electric car (EV) owners who   
OL,11,Fuse "rapid" public charging points were
OL,12,Fpaying almost the same for electricity 
OL,13,Fas they would for petrol per mile.     
OL,15,FCharging the cars at home is cheaper,  
OL,16,Fbut domestic bills are also rising.    
OL,18,FRussia's invasion of Ukraine has been  
OL,19,Fblamed for much of the recent rise in  
OL,20,Felectricity and gas prices.            
